description:
The long awaited and highly acclaimed series is back! CABO the return, Part 2.

At the end of Cabo part 1,Sgt. Major takes Jenni for "training". Miles away from the villa and into hot Mexican heat. Jenni Lee is in for the "training" of her life. The Sgt. dresses her down military style and ties her up hogtied style. In the end she is begging to return to the villa with a new and improved "attitude".

If you missed Cabo one scroll down and watch it; it sets up the entire fantasy we have laid before you. Check out the forums for the inside scoop on this update.
title: Cabo, the Return. Part 2
